South Africa ANC Youth’s Malema Says Supporters Must Respect ANC Process

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-08-30T13:23:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-30/south-africa-anc-youth-s-malema-says-supporters-must-respect-anc-process.html
Julius Malema , the president of
youth wing of  South Africa ’s ruling  African National Congress ,
urged his supporters to respect the disciplinary hearing against
him and the internal processes of the party.  He condemned violence outside the ANC headquarters, where
people have clashed with police during the hearing. Malema spoke
in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
